    <name>Module Goals </name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;ul role="list"&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="1" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{87ea9058-c7dd-4156-af5f-539d4c65b814}{79}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img src="https://lincs-moodle-dev.civicactions.net/pluginfile.php/7064/mod_page/content/3/icon-goals%20%281%29.png" alt="" width="120" height="125" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_right"&gt;Our Purpose:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;The purpose of this module is to identify the variability in adult learners and to present research-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;based learning strategies specific for adults which can&amp;nbsp;increase engagement and access for all&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;learners in Adult Education (AE) classrooms.&amp;nbsp; This module will also define and explain the characteristics of expert learning systems.&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="2" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{87ea9058-c7dd-4156-af5f-539d4c65b814}{82}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Task:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Your task is to reflect on what you already know and do and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;then&amp;nbsp;identify how you could use&amp;nbsp;new research-based strategies from this&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;module to increase the success of your adult learners by incorporating characteristics of expert learning systems in your classroom.&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="3" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{87ea9058-c7dd-4156-af5f-539d4c65b814}{85}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wrap-Up:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;During the final sections of&amp;nbsp;the module, you will be asked to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;review your initial understanding of strategies for teaching adults and then to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;compare what&amp;nbsp;you thought at first to what&amp;nbsp;you think now. Through this&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;process, you will be able to see the growth in your own mindset.&amp;nbsp; Finally,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;you will have the opportunity to complete an assessment to receive a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;certificate of completion.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Divider%20Wave.png" alt="Divider Wave" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
